soul_strike_exps.soul_strike_description: Instantly grant the user Empowered Infusion for ice, and reduce delay of the user's actions for two turns.
Deal three massive physical ice, wind, and holy attacks to one enemy. Can break the damage cap.

Deal ten physical ice and non-elemental attacks to one target, temporarily infuse the user with the power of ice, absorb enemy black magic and white magic abilities cast on the user to restore one ability use each time, and temporarily cause the user's ice abilities to reduce delay of physical attacks of allies in the front row for one turn.

specific.title: Attack with an elemental weakness while the enemy is in its Elements Unbound phase.
